  <div class="container section">
    <h1>Blister Packaging in North York — Never Miss a Dose</h1>
    <p>
      Managing multiple medications is hard. Blister packaging makes it simple — every dose
      labelled by day and time, sealed and ready. At Four Winds Roots Pharmacy, blister packaging
      is included at no extra cost with your prescriptions.
    </p>

    <section aria-labelledby="blister-how-it-works">
      <h2 id="blister-how-it-works">How Blister Packaging Works</h2>
      <ol>
        <li>Tell us you'd like blister packaging — when you call, drop in, or at your next refill.</li>
        <li>We organise all your prescriptions into individual sealed packs, labelled by day and time.</li>
        <li>Pick up your packs or have them delivered — you always know exactly what to take and when.</li>
      </ol>
