      <p>
        Blister packaging is especially valuable for seniors managing several medications,
        caregivers coordinating prescriptions for a family member, and anyone recovering
        from a hospital stay or managing a complex medication schedule.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section aria-labelledby="blister-no-cost">
      <h2 id="blister-no-cost">Included at No Extra Cost</h2>
